        <h1>Welcome to Simple Design</h1>
        <p>Simple Design is a collaboration tool that makes it possible for business analysts/designers, software developers, and users to share a common repository of business processes and documentation.</p>
        <p>Simple Design brings together business documentation with flow diagrams to provide a full picture of your business processes.</p>
        <p>Simple Design is comprised of three parts: a <b>Catalog</b> to organize your business documentation, <b>Artifacts</b> to house the written documentation of your system, and <b>Diagrams</b>, the graphical picture of your system that ties the artifacts together in a meaningful way.</p>
    </div>
